        AIMessage(content="Subject: Long Time, No See – Let’s Catch Up!\n\nHey [Friend’s Name],\n\nI hope this email finds you in great spirits. It’s been far too long since we last caught up, and I’ve been thinking about how you’re doing.\n\nLife on my end has been [brief update about your life – could be work, family, hobbies, etc.]. I’m particularly excited about [something you’re looking forward to], and I’d love to hear what’s new with you!\n\nHave you gone on any new adventures lately? How’s work treating you? Any new hobbies or passions you’ve discovered? I’m all ears for the stories I’ve missed out on.\n\nAlso, I was reminiscing about our last get-together at [a memorable place you both visited or an event you attended], and it brought back so many good memories. We should definitely plan something soon, maybe a [suggestion for a get-together – could be a coffee catch-up, a trip, etc.]?\n\nLet’s not let another year slip by without reconnecting. Tell me a good time for you, and let’s set a date to meet up or have a call.\n\nLooking forward to your reply and hearing all about your life updates.\n\nTake care and talk soon!\n\nWarmest regards,\n[Your Name]"),
